. We combine traditional auction house values with cutting-edge technology to provide an unparalleled experience for buyers and sellers alike.",byTheNumbers:"By the Numbers",yearsOfExcellence:"Years of Excellence",auctionsAnnually:"Auctions Annually",countriesServed:"Countries Served",expertsWorldwide:"Experts Worldwide",ourValues:"Our Values",expertiseTitle:"Expertise",expertiseDesc:"Our specialists bring decades of experience and deep knowledge across all collecting categories.",integrityTitle:"Integrity",integrityDesc:"We maintain the highest standards of authenticity, transparency, and ethical business practices.",innovationTitle:"Innovation",innovationDesc:"We embrace technology to enhance the auction experience while preserving traditional values.",serviceTitle:"Service",serviceDesc:"Personalized attention and exceptional service for every client, from first-time bidders to seasoned collectors.",ourExpertise:"Our Expertise",expertiseDesc2:"Our departments span a wide range of collecting categories, each led by specialists with deep knowledge and passion for their field.",fineArt:"Fine Art",jewelry:"Jewelry & Watches",collectibles:"Collectibles",luxury:"Luxury Goods",globalPresence:"Global Presence",globalDesc:"With offices in major cities worldwide and online bidding available 24/7, we connect buyers and sellers across the globe. Our international team of specialists travels extensively to source exceptional items and provide expert valuations.",joinUs:"Join us in celebrating the art of collecting and discover extraordinary treasures from around the world."},contact:{title:"Contact Us",subtitle:"Get in touch with our team. We're here to help with any questions about our auctions, services, or your collection.",sendMessage:"Send us a Message",name:"Name",email:"Email",phone:"Phone",phoneOptional:"Phone (optional)",subject:"Subject",message:"Message",messagePlaceholder:"Tell us more about your inquiry...",sendButton:"Send Message",contactInfo:"Contact Information",visitUs:"Visit Us",address:"34–35 New Bond Street, London W1A 2AA, UK",callUs:"Call Us",phoneNumber:"+44 20 7293 5000",emailUs:"Email Us",emailAddress:"enquiries@sothebys.com",hours:"Business Hours",hoursText:"Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM",hoursWeekend:"Saturday: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM",hoursClosed:"Sunday: Closed"},faq:{title:"Frequently Asked Questions",subtitle:"Find answers to common questions about bidding, payments, shipping, and our services.",q1:"How do I register to bid?",a1:"Registration is free and takes just a few minutes. Click 'Register' in the top menu, provide your contact information, and verify your email address. For high-value lots, additional verification may be required.",q2:"Can I view items before bidding?",a2:"Yes, we offer preview days before each auction where you can view items in person. Private viewings can also be arranged by appointment. Contact our specialists to schedule a viewing.",q3:"What payment methods do you accept?",a3:"We accept bank transfers, credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express), and certified checks. Payment is due within 7 days of the auction close. A buyer's premium of 25% applies to all purchases.",q4:"What is your return policy?",a4:"Returns are accepted within 14 days if the item significantly differs from its catalog description. The item must be returned in the same condition as received. Refunds will be processed within 10 business days.",q5:"How do I sell items through your auction house?",a5:"Submit your items through our 'Sell With Us' page. Our specialists will review your submission and contact you within 48 hours with a valuation and consignment proposal. We offer competitive commission rates.",q6:"Do you offer international shipping?",a6:"Yes, we ship worldwide. Shipping costs vary by destination and item size. All shipments are fully insured and professionally packed. Customs duties and taxes are the buyer's responsibility."},howToBid:{title:"How to Bid",subtitle:"Your complete guide to participating in our auctions",step:"Step",step1Title:"Register",step1Desc:"Register for free on our platform. Provide your contact information and set up your bidding preferences. Verification is quick and secure.",step2Title:"Browse & Research",step2Desc:"Explore our current auctions and upcoming lots. Review detailed descriptions, high-resolution images, and condition reports for items of interest.",step3Title:"Place Your Bid",step3Desc:"Enter your maximum bid amount. Our system will automatically bid on your behalf up to your limit, ensuring you get the best price.",step4Title:"Win & Pay",step4Desc:"If you win, you'll receive a notification immediately. Payment is due within 7 days. We accept various payment methods for your convenience.",biddingTips:"Bidding Tips",tip1Title:"Set a Budget",tip1Desc:"Decide your maximum bid before the auction starts and stick to it. Factor in the buyer's premium and any applicable taxes.",tip2Title:"Research Thoroughly",tip2Desc:"Review the lot details, condition reports, and provenance. Contact our specialists if you have questions about authenticity or condition.",tip3Title:"Bid Early",tip3Desc:"Don't wait until the last minute. Early bids show serious interest and give you time to adjust your strategy if needed.",auctionTypes:"Auction Types",liveTitle:"Live Auctions",liveDesc:"Participate in real-time bidding with our auctioneer. Bid online, by phone, or in person at our auction room.",onlineTitle:"Online Auctions",onlineDesc:"Browse and bid at your convenience. These auctions run for several days, giving you time to research and decide.",timedTitle:"Timed Auctions",timedDesc:"All lots close at predetermined times. Similar to online auctions but with specific closing schedules for each lot."},shipping:{title:"Shipping & Delivery",subtitle:"Safe, secure, and reliable shipping for your valuable purchases",shippingOptions:"Shipping Options",standardTitle:"Standard Shipping",standardDesc:"Delivery within 5-7 business days",standard