Notifications",bidAlerts:"Bid Alerts",auctionReminders:"Auction Reminders",newsletter:"Newsletter",twoFactorAuth:"Two-Factor Authentication"},terms:{title:"Terms of Service",lastUpdated:"Last Updated",intro:"Welcome to Sotheby's. These Terms of Service govern your use of our website and services. By accessing or using our platform, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree to abide by these terms, please do not use this service.",section1Title:"1. Acceptance of Terms",section1Text:"By accessing and using this website, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by these terms, please do not use this service.",section2Title:"2. Registration and Account",section2Text:"To participate in auctions, you must register for an account. You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information during registration and to update such information to keep it accurate, current, and complete.",section3Title:"3. Bidding and Purchases",section3Text:"All bids are binding. By placing a bid, you agree to purchase the item if you are the winning bidder. A buyer's premium of 25% will be added to the hammer price. Payment is due within 7 days of the auction close.",section4Title:"4. Item Descriptions and Authenticity",section4Text:"We strive to provide accurate descriptions of all items. However, we do not guarantee the accuracy of descriptions and condition reports. All items are sold 'as is' and should be inspected before bidding.",section5Title:"5. Shipping and Delivery",section5Text:"Shipping costs are the responsibility of the buyer unless otherwise stated. We are not responsible for items lost or damaged during shipping, though all shipments are fully insured.",section6Title:"6. Returns and Refunds",section6Text:"Returns are accepted within 14 days if the item significantly differs from its catalog description. The item must be returned in the same condition as received. Refunds will be processed within 10 business days.",section7Title:"7. Privacy",section7Text:"Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy, which also governs your use of our services, to understand our practices.",section8Title:"8. Changes to Terms",section8Text:"We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.",contactInfo:"If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at legal@sothebys.com."},privacy:{title:"Privacy Policy",lastUpdated:"Last Updated",intro:"At Sotheby's, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services.",section1Title:"1. Information We Collect",section1Text:"We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, place a bid, make a purchase, or contact us. This may include your name, email address, phone number, billing address, and payment information.",section2Title:"2. How We Use Your Information",section2Text:"We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services, process transactions, send you technical notices and support messages, and respond to your comments and questions.",section3Title:"3. Sharing of Information",section3Text:"We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information with service providers who assist us in operating our website and conducting our business, as long as those parties agree to keep this information confidential.",section4Title:"4. Data Security",section4Text:"We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.",section5Title:"5. Cookies and Tracking",section5Text:"We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to track activity on our website and hold certain information. You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies or to indicate when a cookie is being sent.",section6Title:"6. Your Rights",section6Text:"You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. You may also object to or restrict certain processing of your information. To exercise these rights, please contact us at privacy@sothebys.com.",section7Title:"7. International Transfers",section7Text:"Your information may be transferred to and maintained on servers located outside of your country. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.",section8Title:"8. Changes to This Policy",section8Text:"We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the 'Last Updated' date.",contactInfo:"If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at privacy@sothebys.com."},cookiePolicy:{title:"Cookie Policy",lastUpdated:"Last Updated",intro:"This Cookie Policy explains how Sotheby's uses cookies and similar technologies to recognize you when you visit our website. It explains what these technologies are and why we use them, as well as your rights to control our use of them.",whatAreCookies:"What Are Cookies?",whatAreCookiesText:"Cookies are small data files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit a website. Cookies are widely used by website owners to make their websites work, or to work more efficiently, as well as to provide reporting information. Cookies set by the website owner (in this case, Sotheby's) are called 'first party cookies'. Cookies set by parties other than the website owner are called 'third party cookies'. Third party cookies enable third party features or functionality to be provided on or through the website.",typesOfCookies:"Types of Cookies We Use",essentialCookies:"Essential Cookies",essentialCookiesText:"These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in, or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work.",analyticsCookies:"Analytics Cookies",analyticsCookiesText:"These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous.",marketingCookies:"Marketing Cookies",marketingCookiesText:"These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device.",preferencesCookies:"Preference Cookies",preferencesCookiesText:"These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalization. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.",managingCookies:"Managing Cookies",managingCookiesText:"You can manage your cookie preferences at any time through our cookie consent banner or by adjusting your browser settings. Most web browsers allow some control of cookies through browser settings. To find out more about cookies, including how to see what cookies have been set, visit www.aboutcookies.org or www.allaboutcookies.org. Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect the functionality of our website and your ability to use certain features.",thirdPartyCookies:"Third Party Cookies",thirdPartyCookiesText:"In addition to our own cookies, we may also use various third party cookies to report usage statistics of the website, deliver advertisements on and through the website, and so on. These third parties may include analytics providers such as Google Analytics, social media platforms, and advertising networks. These third parties have their own privacy policies and may collect information about your online activities over time and across different websites.",updates:"Updates to This Policy",updatesText:"We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time in order to reflect, for example, changes to the cookies we use or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Please therefore revisit this Cookie Policy regularly to stay informed about our use of cookies and related technologies. The date at the top of this Cookie Policy indicates when it was last updated.",moreInfo:"More Information",moreInfoText:"If you have any questions about our use of cookies or other technologies, please contact us at privacy@sothebys.com. We are happy to provide more information about how we protect your privacy and handle your data."},cookieConsent:{title:"We value your privacy",description:"We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience, serve personalized content, and analyze our traffic.",learnMore:"Learn more",acceptAll:"Accept All",rejectAll:"Reject All",customize:"Customize",hideSettings:"Hide Settings",savePreferences:"Save Preferences",essential:"Essential",essentialDesc:"Required for basic website functionality",analytics:"Analytics",analyticsDesc:"Help us understand how visitors interact with our website",marketing:"Marketing",marketingDesc:"Used to deliver personalized advertisements",preferences:"Preferences",preferencesDesc:"Remember your settings and preferences",alwaysActive:"Always Active"},accessibility:{title:"Accessibility Statement",lastUpdated:"Last Updated",intro:"At Sotheby's, we are committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people of all abilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone and applying the relevant accessibility standards to guarantee we provide equal access to all users.",section1Title:"Our Commitment",section1Text:"We strive to ensure that our website and digital platforms are accessible to individuals with disabilities, including those who use assistive technologies. Our goal is to meet or exceed the requirements of the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA standards.",section2Title:"Accessibility Features",section2Text:"Our website includes the following accessibility features:",feature1:"Keyboard navigation support for all interactive elements",feature2:"Alternative text descriptions for images and visual content",feature3:"Clear and consistent navigation structure",feature4:"Sufficient color contrast ratios for text and backgrounds",feature5:"Resizable text without loss of content or functionality",feature6:"Form labels and error messages that are clearly associated",feature7:"Skip navigation links for screen reader users",feature8:"ARIA landmarks and roles for improved screen reader navigation",section3Title:"Assistive Technology Compatibility",section3Text:"Our website is designed to be compatible with the following assistive technologies: screen readers (including JAWS, NVDA, and VoiceOver), screen magnification software, speech recognition software, and keyboard-only navigation. We regularly test our website with these technologies to ensure compatibility.",section4Title:"Ongoing Efforts",section4Text:"We view accessibility as an ongoing effort. Our team regularly reviews and updates our website to improve accessibility. We conduct regular accessibility audits, provide accessibility training to our staff, incorporate accessibility into our design and development processes, and actively seek feedback from users with disabilities.",section5Title:"Third-Party Content",section5Text:"While we strive to ensure accessibility of our website, we acknowledge that some third-party content or applications may not be fully accessible. We are working with our partners and vendors to improve the accessibility of third-party content where possible.",section6Title:"Alternative Access",section6Text:"If you encounter any accessibility barriers on our website, we are happy to provide information in alternative formats upon request. Please contact our accessibility team, and we will work to provide the information you need in a format that is accessible to you.",section7Title:"Feedback and Contact",section7Text:"We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of our website. If you encounter any accessibility barriers or have suggestions for improvement, please contact us. Your feedback helps us improve the accessibility of our website for all users.",contactInfo:"For accessibility-related inquiries or to report accessibility issues, please contact us at accessibility@sothebys.com or call our dedicated accessibility line at +1 (800) 555-0199. We aim to respond to all accessibility feedback within 2 business days."},buyersGuide:{title:"Buyer's Guide",subtitle:"Everything you need to know about buying at Sotheby's auctions",intro:"Welcome to Sotheby's. Whether you're a first-time bidder or an experienced collector, this comprehensive guide will help you navigate the auction process with confidence. From registration to receiving your purchase, we're here to make your experience seamless and enjoyable.",section1Title:"Getting Started",section1Text:"To participate in our auctions, you'll first need to create an account on our website. Registration is free and takes only a few minutes. You'll need to provide your contact information, a valid email address, and payment details for verification purposes.",registrationSteps:"Registration Steps:",step1:"Click 'Sign Up' in the top right corner of the website",step2:"Enter your email address and create a secure password",step3:"Complete your profile with your full name and contact details",step4:"Verify your email address through the confirmation link",step5:"Add a payment method to enable bidding",section2Title:"Understanding Auctions",section2Text:"Our auctions feature a wide range of exceptional items across multiple categories. Each lot is carefully vetted by our expert specialists who provide detailed descriptions, condition reports, and provenance information. Take time to review all available information before placing your bid.",estimateTitle:"Auction Estimates",estimateText:"Each lot includes a low and high estimate, representing our specialists' opinion of the range within which the lot might sell. Estimates are not guarantees of final sale prices.",reserveTitle:"Reserve Prices",reserveText:"Some lots have a confidential reserve price—the minimum price at which the lot may be sold. If bidding doesn't reach the reserve, the lot will not be sold.",section3Title:"How to Bid",section3Text:"Bidding at Sotheby's is straightforward. Once registered, you can place bids on any lot. Remember that all bids are binding commitments to purchase the item if you are the winning bidder.",bidStep1Title:"Browse and Research",bidStep1Text:"Review lot descriptions, condition reports, and images carefully. Contact our specialists if you have questions.",bidStep2Title:"Set Your Budget",bidStep2Text:"Determine your maximum bid amount, including the buyer's premium (25%) and any applicable taxes and shipping costs.",bidStep3Title:"Place Your Bid",bidStep3Text:"Enter your bid amount and confirm. You'll receive confirmation and be notified if you're outbid.",section4Title:"Payment",section4Text:"If you're the winning bidder, payment is due within 7 days of the auction close. We accept major credit cards, wire transfers, and approved financing options. The final price includes the hammer price plus a 25% buyer's premium.",paymentMethods:"Accepted Payment Methods:",payment1:"Visa, Mastercard, American Express",payment2:"Wire transfer (bank transfer)",payment3:"Certified check or cashier's check",payment4:"Financing available for qualifying purchases",section5Title:"Shipping & Delivery",section5Text:"We offer worldwide shipping for all purchases. Our experienced art handlers ensure your items are professionally packed and shipped with full insurance coverage. Shipping costs vary based on item size, weight, and destination.",domestic:"Domestic",domesticTime:"5-7 business days",international:"International",internationalTime:"10-14 business days",express:"Express",expressTime:"2-3 business days",section6Title:"Authenticity Guarantee",section6Text:"Every item sold through Sotheby's comes with our authenticity guarantee. Our specialists thoroughly examine and authenticate all items before they are offered for sale. If an item is found to be inauthentic, you may return it for a full refund within five years of purchase, subject to our terms and conditions.",needHelp:"Need Help?",contactInfo:"Our Client Services team is available to assist you with any questions. Contact us at clientservices@sothebys.com or call +1 (800) 555-0199. We're available Monday through Friday, 9am to 6pm EST."},search:{title:"Search",subtitle:"Find your perfect lot",placeholder:"Search for lots, categories, or artists...",searching:"Searching...",noResults:"No results found",tryDifferent:"Try different keywords",result:"result",results:"results",resultsFound:"results found",viewAll:"View All Results",randomPicks:"You Might Like",searchResults:"Search Results",loading:"Loading...",scrollForMore:"Scroll for more results...",noResultsDesc:"Try different keywords or browse our categories"},bid:{title:"Place Your Bid",currentBid:"Current Bid",yourBid:"Your Bid",minimumBid:"Minimum Bid",enterBid:"Enter your bid amount",placeBid:"Place Bid",bidPlaced:"Bid Placed Successfully",bidError:"Error placing bid",outbid:"You've been outbid",winning:"You're winning",auctionEnded:"Auction has ended",timeRemaining:"Time Remai